  "gettingHere": {
    "directions": "From Larnaca Airport, take the A3 motorway east to Ayia Napa. Continue on the coastal road B3 heading north toward Paralimni. Follow signs for Paralimni Coast / Thalassa Beach. Turn left onto Thalassa Lane just after the small white chapel. The studio building is right at the end of the lane with a blue gate.",
    "parking": "Small private car park at the end of Thalassa Lane — space for 1 car per studio. Your space is marked '1A'.",
    "publicTransport": "The nearest bus stop is on the main coastal road, a 10-minute walk away. Route 101 connects to Protaras and Ayia Napa.",
    "taxi": "Recommended: Paralimni Cabs (+357 23 821 999). Around 45 minutes from Larnaca Airport."
  },
  "houseRules": [
    "No smoking inside — terrace only",
    "No parties or events — quiet hours 11pm to 8am",
    "Maximum occupancy: 2 guests",
    "No pets allowed",
    "Clean dishes immediately and keep the kitchen counter clear — Cyprus's warm weather can attract insects",
    "Please use the bin next to the toilet — do not flush toilet paper (Cyprus plumbing cannot handle it)",
    "Place the metallic key in the electricity plug by the door when inside; remove it every time you leave",
    "Close terrace door and windows when air conditioning is running",
    "Return keys to the keybox and reset the code at checkout",
    "Treat the apartment with care — please report any breakages promptly"
